    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds more like it. people always say \"it gets better\" or \"keep fighting,\" but they don't get it. they don't understand that the fighting is what hurts. if i'm just fundamentally flawed like you say... then what's even the point of trying to keep going? it just feels like a waste of energy.",
